    "title": "The gun of the Bulls.",
    "description": "Always non-elemental.\n\nCosts 1 SMG round per shot; has a 60% chance to fire an extra projectile (2 total). While aiming, fires a 9-14 round Dahl burst. Projectiles follow a distinctive bull-like pattern. Greatly reduced recoil, with slightly reduced accuracy."
  },
  "notes": "Fixed spawn in Frostburn Canyon, making it easy to farm. It does not scale in Normal Mode, or in TVHM until the story is finished.\nStrong on Gaige: Close Enough and Anarchy reduce the need for accuracy, and the fast empty-reload rhythm suits her.\nStocks matter little (aside from a Dahl stock adding +1 burst); grip and accessory have the biggest impact.\nLonger fights: Dahl grip with Flying is strong sustained DPS. Short fights: Flying or Stopping with Bandit or Maliwan grip.\nNon-elemental, but reliable crits make it effective against Loaders up close.\nCan remain useful in UVHM, but level scaling still matters for damage.",
